#: ../../C/CRC-handbook.rst:5
msgid "CRC handbook"
msgstr "CRC handbook"

#: ../../C/CRC-handbook.rst:7
msgid ""
"Any of the editions of the *Chemical Rubber Company Handbook of Chemistry "
"and Physics*\\; there are other CRC handbooks, such as the *CRC Standard "
"Mathematical Tables and Formulae*\\, but \"the\" CRC handbook is the "
"chemistry and physics reference. It is massive tome full of mathematical "
"tables, physical constants of thousands of alloys and chemical compounds, "
"dielectric strengths, vapor pressure, resistivity, and the like. Hackers "
"have remarkably little actual use for these sorts of arcana, but are such "
"information junkies that a large percentage of them acquire copies anyway "
"and would feel vaguely bereft if they couldn't look up the magnetic "
"susceptibility of potassium permanganate at a moment's notice. On hackers' "
"bookshelves, the CRC handbook is rather likely to keep company with an "
"unabridged Oxford English Dictionary and a good atlas."
msgstr ""
"『Chemical Rubber Company Handbook of Chemistry and Physics』のいずれかの版のこと。『CRC "
"Standard Mathematical Tables and "
"Formulae』など他のCRCハンドブックもありますが、「ザ・」CRCハンドブックといえばこの化学・物理学のリファレンスです。これは数学の表、何千もの合金や化合物の物理定数、誘電強度、蒸気圧、抵抗率などで埋め尽くされた巨大な大冊です。ハッカーはこの種の難解な知識を実際にはほとんど使いませんが、彼らは情報中毒なので、その大多数はとにかく一冊手に入れ、過マンガン酸カリウムの磁化率をいつでもすぐに調べられないと漠然とした喪失感を覚えるのです。ハッカーの本棚では、CRCハンドブックは縮約なしのオックスフォード英語辞典や良質な地図帳と仲良く並んでいる可能性がかなり高いでしょう。"
